reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The size is great!
reviews.reviewText: I got this for my father, who let's face it is not technologically inclined..lol. It is perfect! The size is great, the updates are free and it's very easy to use. You can do everything on this just as you would on your phone. He loves it. It's perfect for those who need a bigger screen!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Accurate and multifunctional!!
reviews.reviewText: Great for older cars without built in GPS since most older cars don't have Bluetooth. Audio can be from audio jack or wireless through the FM. After searching for satellite signals you are good to go! MicroSD slot allows to add media like MP3 and photo. Come pre-installed with maps and a site to download updated maps as needed. The Sunshield is a great addition along with the suction cup window mount. Internal battery allows for pedestrian mode also! Can use for camping. Not pictured comes with USB cord and 12v cigarette lighter adapter to power/charge.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This product is amazing. It has a very large display and is very bright. I had to turn it down because of how bright it was. The navigation is on point and I had not trouble be-bopping around with it helping me navigate where I needed to go!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars This unit did not work right out of the box.
reviews.reviewText: I am paying for a product to work right out of the box. This unit would not initialize even after pushing the factory reset button. This is the second GPS unit that I have returned from this company, neither one worked. I am not wasting my time with their, English as a second language, customer service representatives fixing a problem that should not have existed in the first place.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: We used this to travel out of state. My phones gps went absolutely crazy and tried to send us 55 mins the other way but the GPS was right on spot and was super full helpful and easy to pull up. I absolutely LOVE this product

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Just what we needed. It comes with a lot more then just a GPS. I'm amazed. I've plaids around with it in the house and can't wait to try in the car today and for future trips. Clear screen easy to navigate the apps.
